      "dateModified": "2026-07-01",
      "description": "Renewal Radar is Sighub's HubSpot app. It scans renewal signals across HubSpot CRM objects (deals, quotes, line items, subscriptions, contracts, custom objects, and customer activity), finds renewal timing spread across HubSpot data, and creates one self-resolving HubSpot task per real risk with the evidence attached. Renewal Radar is deterministic and auditable. It uses no AI, no churn prediction, and no health score. It reads metadata only and never reads email content, notes, call recordings, or ticket content.",
